<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 10:07:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>当地负责人称，俄罗斯在北奥塞梯上空摧毁了三架乌克兰无人机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-destroys-three-ukrainian-drones-over-north-ossetia-local-head-says/articleshow/110817653.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110817653.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯防空部队在北奥塞梯-阿拉尼亚共和国莫兹多克摧毁了三架乌克兰无人机，造成轻微损坏和火灾。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 09:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-destroys-three-ukrainian-drones-over-north-ossetia-local-head-says/articleshow/110817653.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其对中国进口汽车征收40%关税</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/turkey-imposes-40-tariff-on-vehicle-imports-from-china/articleshow/110817387.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110817387.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;土耳其政府专注于增加生产和出口，以解决去年 452 亿美元的经常账户赤字。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 09:04:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/turkey-imposes-40-tariff-on-vehicle-imports-from-china/articleshow/110817387.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯监禁因收集军事数据而被拘留的法国公民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-jails-french-citizen-detained-on-charges-of-collecting-military-data/articleshow/110817214.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110817214.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国公民洛朗·维纳蒂尔 (Laurent Vinatier) 因在马克龙关于在乌克兰部署军队的言论而与巴黎关系紧张之际，因收集有关俄​​罗斯军事问题的信息而被下令关押在莫斯科的监狱中。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 08:53:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-jails-french-citizen-detained-on-charges-of-collecting-military-data/articleshow/110817214.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦教师因在穆扎法尔加尔强奸两名未成年男孩而被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pak-teacher-arrested-for-raping-of-two-minor-boys-in-muzaffargarh/articleshow/110816785.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110816785.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;根据非营利组织 Sahil 与巴基斯坦儿童基金会合作发布的“2023 年残酷数字”报告，巴基斯坦 2023 年报告的虐待儿童案件达到惊人的 4,213 起，平均每天有 11 名儿童面临虐待，令人震惊。国家人权委员会（NCHR）。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 08:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pak-teacher-arrested-for-raping-of-two-minor-boys-in-muzaffargarh/articleshow/110816785.cms</guid></item><item><title>荷兰称中国战斗机“不安全”地接近荷兰船只</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/chinese-fighter-jets-approached-dutch-ship-unsafely-netherlands-says/articleshow/110816562.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110816562.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国空军战机在东海环绕一艘荷兰护卫舰并接近一架荷兰直升机，在支持联合国对朝鲜制裁的巡逻期间造成潜在的不安全局势。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 08:23:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/chinese-fighter-jets-approached-dutch-ship-unsafely-netherlands-says/articleshow/110816562.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国将以色列和哈马斯列入侵犯儿童行为的国家名单</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-adds-israel-hamas-in-list-of-states-committing-violations-against-children/articleshow/110816032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110816032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国已将以色列和哈马斯列入针对儿童犯罪的国家名单。以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡批评联合国支持哈马斯，导致与以色列关系紧张。伊斯雷尔·卡茨警告说，与联合国的关系紧张。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 08:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-adds-israel-hamas-in-list-of-states-committing-violations-against-children/articleshow/110816032.cms</guid></item><item><title>马克龙谴责对丹麦首相的“不可接受”袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/macron-condemns-unacceptable-attack-on-danish-pm/articleshow/110816418.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110816418.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国总统马克龙周六谴责丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森在哥本哈根被一名男子袭击的事件是“不可接受的”。马克龙在 X（前推特）上发帖称：“对丹麦首相的攻击是不可接受的。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 08:14:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/macron-condemns-unacceptable-attack-on-danish-pm/articleshow/110816418.cms</guid></item><item><title>救援人员在希腊岛上搜寻英国电视医生已连续第三天</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/rescuers-search-for-british-tv-doctor-for-a-third-day-on-greek-island/articleshow/110815981.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110815981.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国电视节目主持人迈克尔·莫斯利 (Michael Mosley) 在炎热的气温下沿着岩石海岸小道漫步时失踪，救援人员正在希腊山区的锡米岛寻找他。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 07:48:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/rescuers-search-for-british-tv-doctor-for-a-third-day-on-greek-island/articleshow/110815981.cms</guid></item><item><title>袭击丹麦首相弗雷德里克森的嫌疑人将面临初步审讯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/suspect-to-face-preliminary-questioning-after-assault-on-danish-pm-frederiksen/articleshow/110815606.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110815606.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;丹麦警方正在调查哥本哈根市中心发生的针对总理梅特·弗雷德里克森的袭击事件。事件发生在库尔托维特广场，弗雷德里克森在那里遭到一名身份不明的男子袭击。她在袭击中毫发无伤。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 07:31:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/suspect-to-face-preliminary-questioning-after-assault-on-danish-pm-frederiksen/articleshow/110815606.cms</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚以安全考虑为驱逐海洋游牧民族的行为辩护</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/malaysia-defends-eviction-of-sea-nomads-citing-security-concerns/articleshow/110812080.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110812080.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马来西亚当局以安全和反犯罪措施为由，将 500 多名巴瑶族海上游牧民从沙巴仙本那区的家中驱逐。批评者认为此举危及无国籍社区。沙巴部长声称，驱逐行动针对的是非法活动，一些居民烧毁了自己的房屋以示同情。人权组织敦促政府提供替代住房并解决文件问题。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 04:18:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/malaysia-defends-eviction-of-sea-nomads-citing-security-concerns/articleshow/110812080.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国警惕来自朝鲜的更多垃圾气球</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-on-alert-for-more-trash-balloons-from-the-north/articleshow/110815270.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110815270.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;韩国军方表示，他们对周日可能从朝鲜运来的更多携带垃圾的气球保持警惕。平壤周日宣布停止发放气球，但几天后，一个名为“自由朝鲜战士”的韩国组织表示，已发送了 10 个带有韩国流行音乐的气球和 20 万份反对领导人金正恩的传单。韩国军方正在“保持警惕地密切监视”，因为周六“可能会有更多垃圾气球降落”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 07:16:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-on-alert-for-more-trash-balloons-from-the-north/articleshow/110815270.cms</guid></item><item><title>“结婚的第一步”：日本推出约会应用程序以提高生育率</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/first-step-to-marriage-hunting-japan-launches-dating-app-to-boost-fertility-rate/articleshow/110813885.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110813885.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;为了帮助应对日本不断下降的生育率，东京官员设计了一款人工智能驱动的约会应用程序，该应用程序将于今年年底上线。该应用程序得到了埃隆·马斯克的赞赏，他称其为“激进的行动”。马斯克在 X 上发帖称：“我很高兴日本政府认识到此事的重要性。如果不采取激进行动，日本（以及许多其他国家）将会消失！”</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 07:05:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/first-step-to-marriage-hunting-japan-launches-dating-app-to-boost-fertility-rate/articleshow/110813885.cms</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织：斯里兰卡在债务重组方面取得“强劲进展”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lanka-has-made-strong-progress-on-debt-restructuring-front-imf/articleshow/110814896.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110814896.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;国际货币基金组织表示，斯里兰卡的宏观经济政策改革已开始显现成效，预计很快将与外部商业债权人达成协议。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 06:55:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lanka-has-made-strong-progress-on-debt-restructuring-front-imf/articleshow/110814896.cms</guid></item><item><title>白俄罗斯表示，如果华沙发送信息，将调查一名波兰士兵的死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/belarus-says-it-will-investigate-a-polish-soldiers-death-if-warsaw-sends-information/articleshow/110814208.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110814208.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;白俄罗斯当局愿意调查一名在边境被刺伤的波兰士兵的死亡事件，但缺乏波兰方面的必要信息。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 06:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/belarus-says-it-will-investigate-a-polish-soldiers-death-if-warsaw-sends-information/articleshow/110814208.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗直升机坠毁事件表明德黑兰对老化机队的依赖及其国内挑战</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-helicopter-crash-shows-tehrans-reliance-on-an-aging-fleet-as-well-as-its-challenges-at-home/articleshow/110813054.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110813054.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西 (Ebrahim Raisi) 在阿塞拜疆-伊朗边境附近发生直升机坠毁事故，引发人们对贝尔 212 直升机在恶劣天气条件下安全性的质疑。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 05:14:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-helicopter-crash-shows-tehrans-reliance-on-an-aging-fleet-as-well-as-its-challenges-at-home/articleshow/110813054.cms</guid></item><item><title>热浪席卷美国西南部，气温创历史新高，预计气温将达到三位数</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/heat-wave-grips-southwest-us-as-records-tumble-more-triple-digit-temperatures-forecast/articleshow/110812296.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110812296.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国西南部正在经历一场严重的热浪，气温破纪录地超过 110 华氏度。美国国家气象局向亚利桑那州和内华达州等地区发布了高温警报。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 04:55:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/heat-wave-grips-southwest-us-as-records-tumble-more-triple-digit-temperatures-forecast/articleshow/110812296.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗拥有“1971 年推文”，并与视频保持距离</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/ex-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-owns-up-to-1971-tweet-distances-himself-from-video/articleshow/110811983.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110811983.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗承认发表了“反军事”帖子，并对穆吉布的言论感到遗憾。他以经济困境为由批评了人民民主党政府的变革。汗的社交媒体团队于5月26日上传了这些帖子，质疑谁是真正的叛徒。他进一步表示，报告强调了两个目标——追究达卡陷落的责任，并提出措施确保类似错误不再重演。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 04:43:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/ex-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-owns-up-to-1971-tweet-distances-himself-from-video/articleshow/110811983.cms</guid></item><item><title>赞比亚法院以网络犯罪罪判处22名中国公民长期监禁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/zambian-court-sentences-22-chinese-nationals-to-long-prison-terms-for-cybercrimes/articleshow/110812505.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110812505.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 04:42:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/zambian-court-sentences-22-chinese-nationals-to-long-prison-terms-for-cybercrimes/articleshow/110812505.cms</guid></item><item><title>加拿大汽车零部件亿万富翁 Frank Stronach，91 岁，因性侵犯指控被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canadian-auto-parts-billionaire-frank-stronach-91-arrested-on-sexual-assault-charges/articleshow/110811783.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110811783.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 91 岁的奥地利裔加拿大汽车零部件亿万富翁 Frank Stronach 因性侵犯指控被皮尔地区警方逮捕。这些指控包括强奸、非礼、性侵犯和强迫监禁。与家人的法律纠纷已得到解决。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 03:56:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canadian-auto-parts-billionaire-frank-stronach-91-arrested-on-sexual-assault-charges/articleshow/110811783.cms</guid></item><item><title>越南逮捕两名知名 Facebook 用户，指控其滥用民主自由</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vietnam-arrests-two-well-known-facebook-users-over-democratic-freedom-abuse/articleshow/110811680.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110811680.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;越南逮捕张辉山和陈廷俊，原因是他们在领导层改组和媒体审查期间在 Facebook 上批评当局。新警察部长批准后，账户失踪引发逮捕谣言。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 03:46:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vietnam-arrests-two-well-known-facebook-users-over-democratic-freedom-abuse/articleshow/110811680.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>